f\in L^2(\Omega).
 \begin{cases} &-k_i\Delta u_i=f,x\in \Omega_i, i=1,2\\ &u_i=0, x\in \partial \Omega\\ & u_1=u_2, x \in \Gamma\\ &k_1 \nabla u_1 \cdot n = k_2 \nabla u_2 \cdot n, x \in \Gamma \end{cases} 
